HEADWORD: Stinkard
<hw>Stink"ard</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A mean,
stinking, paltry fellow.</def> <rj><au>B. Jonson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>The teledu of the East Indies. It
emits a disagreeable odor.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Stinkball</ent>⟦br⟧
